  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-03-23",
    "date": "2021-06-08T12:50:21Z",
    "text": "Hire Veteran Health Heroes Act of 2021\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to consult with the Department of Defense to identify members of the Armed Forces in health care occupations who are separating from the Armed Forces.\n\nThe VA must refer interested members to a recruiter for consideration of open positions in the member's specialty and geography of interest."
